---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Gen Yang" description="Background and experience in software engineering and quantitative finance" image="/gen-yang-profile.jpg">
  <div class="page">
    <h1>$ cat ~/about.md</h1>
    
    <div class="profile-header">
      <div class="profile-image">
        <img src="/gen-yang-profile.jpg" alt="Gen Yang Profile Picture" />
      </div>
      <div class="profile-intro">
        <h2>## About Gen Yang</h2>
        <p>
          I'm Gen Yang, a software engineer with a deep fascination for high-performance computing and quantitative finance. 
          My journey began with traditional software development, but I've progressively moved toward the intersection 
          of technology and finance, where microseconds matter and precision is paramount.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-section">
      <h2>## Technical Expertise</h2>
      <div class="code-block">
        <pre><code>{`const skills = {
  languages: ["C++", "Python", "JavaScript", "TypeScript"],
  systems: {
    lowLatency: "Ultra-fast market data processing",
    networking: "DPDK, kernel-bypass optimization", 
    storage: "High-performance I/O with io_uring"
  },
  web: {
    frontend: ["React", "Astro", "Modern CSS"],
    backend: ["Node.js", "RESTful APIs", "WebSockets"],
    deployment: ["Vercel", "CI/CD workflows"]
  },
  finance: {
    trading: "Algorithmic strategy development",
    data: "Tick-by-tick market analysis",
    risk: "Portfolio optimization and risk management"
  }
};`}</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-section">
      <h2>## Current Focus</h2>
      <p>
        I'm currently building a comprehensive high-frequency trading system that combines cutting-edge 
        C++ performance with modern web technologies. This project serves as both a learning endeavor 
        and a practical exploration of ultra-low-latency systems engineering.
      </p>
      
      <ul class="focus-list">
        <li><strong>Low-Latency Systems:</strong> Implementing kernel-bypass networking with DPDK for microsecond-level market data processing</li>
        <li><strong>Backtesting Framework:</strong> Developing high-fidelity simulation capabilities with realistic market microstructure modeling</li>
        <li><strong>Real-time Monitoring:</strong> Creating web-based dashboards for system performance and trading metrics</li>
        <li><strong>Risk Management:</strong> Building comprehensive portfolio monitoring and risk assessment tools</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-section">
      <h2>## Philosophy</h2>
      <blockquote>
        "In the world of high-frequency trading, every nanosecond counts. But beyond raw speed, 
        it's the elegance of the solution and the robustness of the system that truly matter."
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-section">
      <h2>## Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Interested in discussing low-latency systems, quantitative finance, or modern web development? 
        Feel free to reach out through any of the channels below.
      </p>
      
      <div class="contact-links">
        <p><code>$ find ~/contact -type f</code></p>
        <ul>
          <li>ðŸ“§ <strong>Email:</strong> gen.yang@example.com</li>
          <li>ðŸ’» <strong>GitHub:</strong> github.com/genyang</li>
          <li>ðŸ”— <strong>LinkedIn:</strong> linkedin.com/in/gen-yang</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .profile-header {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.03);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .profile-header {
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
  
  .profile-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .profile-image img {
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 3px solid var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.2);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .profile-image img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.3);
  }
  
  .profile-intro {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .profile-intro {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
  
  .profile-intro h2 {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  
  .terminal-section {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    background: rgba(238, 195, 94, 0.05);
  }
  
  .code-block {
    background: rgba(238, 195, 94, 0.1);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  
  .code-block pre {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  
  .focus-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .focus-list li {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .focus-list li::before {
    content: "â–¶ ";
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: bold;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }
  
  blockquote {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  .contact-links ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .contact-links li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }
</style>